### ============================================
### SAP SuccessFactors RBP Audit API - PHASE 2 TESTS
### Testing real SF API integration
### ============================================

### 1. Service Metadata
GET http://localhost:4004/odata/v4/audit/$metadata

### ============================================
### 2. RUN AUDIT ACTIONS (Now with real SF data)
### ============================================

### 2.1 Run FULL Audit (extract all)
POST http://localhost:4004/odata/v4/audit/runAudit
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "instance": "QAS",
  "mode": "FULL",
  "sampleSize": 5,
  "extractMembers": true,
  "extractRoles": true
}

### 2.2 Run SAMPLE Audit (limited groups for testing)
POST http://localhost:4004/odata/v4/audit/runAudit
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "instance": "QAS",
  "mode": "SAMPLE",
  "sampleSize": 3,
  "extractMembers": true,
  "extractRoles": true
}

### 2.3 Run Audit - Members Only
POST http://localhost:4004/odata/v4/audit/runAudit
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "instance": "QAS",
  "mode": "SAMPLE",
  "sampleSize": 3,
  "extractMembers": true,
  "extractRoles": false
}

### 2.4 Run Audit - Roles Only
POST http://localhost:4004/odata/v4/audit/runAudit
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "instance": "QAS",
  "mode": "SAMPLE",
  "sampleSize": 3,
  "extractMembers": false,
  "extractRoles": true
}

### ============================================
### 3. GET AUDIT STATUS
### ============================================

### 3.1 Get Latest Audit
POST http://localhost:4004/odata/v4/audit/getLatestAudit
Content-Type: application/json

{}

### 3.2 Get All Audit Headers
GET http://localhost:4004/odata/v4/audit/AuditHeaders?$orderby=GeneratedOn desc

### 3.3 Get Completed Audits Only
GET http://localhost:4004/odata/v4/audit/AuditHeaders?$filter=Status eq 'Completed'&$orderby=GeneratedOn desc

### ============================================
### 4. VERIFY EXTRACTED DATA (After audit completes)
### ============================================

### 4.1 Get All Permission Groups
GET http://localhost:4004/odata/v4/audit/PermissionGroups?$top=20

### 4.2 Get Static Groups
GET http://localhost:4004/odata/v4/audit/PermissionGroups?$filter=StaticOrDynamic eq 'STATIC'

### 4.3 Get Dynamic Groups
GET http://localhost:4004/odata/v4/audit/PermissionGroups?$filter=StaticOrDynamic eq 'DYNAMIC'

### 4.4 Get Large Groups (>50 members)
GET http://localhost:4004/odata/v4/audit/PermissionGroups?$filter=TotalMemberCount gt 50

### ============================================
### 5. USER DATA
### ============================================

### 5.1 Get All Users
GET http://localhost:4004/odata/v4/audit/Users?$top=20

### 5.2 Get Active Users
GET http://localhost:4004/odata/v4/audit/Users?$filter=Status eq 'active'&$top=20

### 5.3 Get Inactive Users
GET http://localhost:4004/odata/v4/audit/Users?$filter=Status eq 'inactive'&$top=20

### ============================================
### 6. GROUP MEMBERSHIPS
### ============================================

### 6.1 Get All Memberships
GET http://localhost:4004/odata/v4/audit/GroupMemberships?$top=50

### 6.2 Get Memberships with User and Group details (using expand)
GET http://localhost:4004/odata/v4/audit/GroupMemberships?$top=20&$expand=User,Group

### 6.3 Get Members of a Specific Group
# @prompt groupID
GET http://localhost:4004/odata/v4/audit/GroupMemberships?$filter=GroupID eq {{groupID}}&$expand=User

### ============================================
### 7. ROLES DATA
### ============================================

### 7.1 Get All Roles
GET http://localhost:4004/odata/v4/audit/RBPRoles?$top=20

### 7.2 Get Role by ID
# @prompt roleID
GET http://localhost:4004/odata/v4/audit/RBPRoles('{{roleID}}')

### ============================================
### 8. ANALYTICS - Multi-Group Users
### ============================================

### 8.1 Get All Multi-Group Users
GET http://localhost:4004/odata/v4/audit/MultiGroupUsers?$top=20

### 8.2 Get High Risk Users
GET http://localhost:4004/odata/v4/audit/MultiGroupUsers?$filter=RiskLevel eq 'High'&$expand=User

### 8.3 Get Medium Risk Users
GET http://localhost:4004/odata/v4/audit/MultiGroupUsers?$filter=RiskLevel eq 'Medium'&$expand=User

### 8.4 Get Users with Most Groups (sorted)
GET http://localhost:4004/odata/v4/audit/MultiGroupUsers?$orderby=GroupCount desc&$top=10&$expand=User

### ============================================
### 9. ANALYTICS - Group Size Distribution
### ============================================

### 9.1 Get Group Size Distribution
GET http://localhost:4004/odata/v4/audit/GroupSizeDistribution

### 9.2 Get Large Groups (100+ members)
GET http://localhost:4004/odata/v4/audit/GroupSizeDistribution?$filter=Bucket eq 'SIZE_100_PLUS'

### 9.3 Get Specific Bucket for an Audit
# Replace with actual AuditID from step 3.2
# @prompt auditID
GET http://localhost:4004/odata/v4/audit/GroupSizeDistribution(Bucket='SIZE_100_PLUS',parent_AuditID_AuditID={{auditID}})

### ============================================
### 10. ANALYTICS - User Group Count Distribution
### ============================================

### 10.1 Get User Group Count Distribution
GET http://localhost:4004/odata/v4/audit/UserGroupCountDistribution

### 10.2 Get Users with 8+ groups
GET http://localhost:4004/odata/v4/audit/UserGroupCountDistribution?$filter=Bucket eq 'EIGHT_PLUS'

### ============================================
### 11. UNUSED ROLES
### ============================================

### 11.1 Get Unused Roles (roles with no target population)
GET http://localhost:4004/odata/v4/audit/UnusedRoles?$expand=Role

### ============================================
### 12. USER ROLE ASSIGNMENTS
### ============================================

### 12.1 Get User Role Assignments
GET http://localhost:4004/odata/v4/audit/UserRoleAssignments?$top=20&$expand=User,Role

### ============================================
### 13. ADVANCED QUERIES
### ============================================

### 13.1 Get Users in both "Admin" and "Super Admins" groups
GET http://localhost:4004/odata/v4/audit/MultiGroupUsers?$filter=GroupNames contains 'Admin'&$expand=User

### 13.2 Get Group Membership Count per User (using $apply)
GET http://localhost:4004/odata/v4/audit/GroupMemberships?$apply=groupby((UserID),aggregate(GroupID with countdistinct as GroupCount))&$orderby=GroupCount desc

### 13.3 Get Users with their Groups (using expand)
GET http://localhost:4004/odata/v4/audit/Users?$top=5&$expand=GroupMemberships/Group

### 13.4 Get Groups with their Members (using expand)
GET http://localhost:4004/odata/v4/audit/PermissionGroups?$top=5&$expand=GroupMemberships/User

### ============================================
### 14. BATCH REQUESTS (for multiple queries)
### ============================================

POST http://localhost:4004/odata/v4/audit/$batch
Content-Type: multipart/mixed; boundary=batch_123

--batch_123
Content-Type: application/http
Content-Transfer-Encoding: binary

GET AuditHeaders?$top=1 HTTP/1.1
Host: localhost:4004


--batch_123
Content-Type: application/http
Content-Transfer-Encoding: binary

GET PermissionGroups?$top=5 HTTP/1.1
Host: localhost:4004


--batch_123
Content-Type: application/http
Content-Transfer-Encoding: binary

GET MultiGroupUsers?$top=5&$expand=User HTTP/1.1
Host: localhost:4004


--batch_123--

### ============================================
### 15. AUDIT SIGN-OFF
### ============================================

### 15.1 Get Audit Sign-Off
GET http://localhost:4004/odata/v4/audit/AuditSignOff

### ============================================
### 16. ADMIN SERVICE (requires authentication)
### ============================================

### 16.1 Admin - Get Audit Headers
GET http://localhost:4004/odata/v4/admin/AuditHeaders

### 16.2 Admin - Get Audit Sign-Off
GET http://localhost:4004/odata/v4/admin/AuditSignOff